== Overview ==
The Ranger class wheeler is the smallest and lightest available bot chassis for controllers. It is also the fastest and most maneuverable, able to dodge enemy fire and outrun the more powerful chassis. A special feature of the Ranger is its single fully rotatable turret giving it exceptional accuracy. In combat the Ranger speeds in close and targets key points on its enemies, giving it a higher chance of inflicting critical hits.

Sells for 9800 credits.

